# Obsessions agent rules

Read [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) for the full contract.

## Stack

Next.js 15 App Router, Supabase (Auth/Postgres/Storage), Tailwind, Framer Motion, Zustand, Vitest.

## Before every PR

```bash
npm run lint && npm run test:run && npm run build
```

## Invariants

- Waitlist-only: no public sign-up UI or `signUp` flows
- Keep RLS on entries, images, waitlist
- Never commit secrets or edit `supabase/migrations/` without `human-approved` label
- JSX text: avoid unescaped apostrophes (use template strings)

## Branches & PRs

- Branch: `cursor/issue-<n>-<slug>`
- Label PR: `agent-pr`
- Do not auto-merge if touching middleware, auth, supabase migrations, or fonts

## Conventions

- Match existing patterns in surrounding files; minimal scope
- Entry layout: [EntryCard.tsx](../../src/components/EntryCard.tsx), timeline: [TimelineView.tsx](../../src/components/TimelineView.tsx)
- Deploy skill: [.cursor/skills/deploy/SKILL.md](../skills/deploy/SKILL.md)
